const AboutMe = () => { return(

Hello!

My name is Michelle Yang.

I am a recent graduate of a software engineering bootcamp. I am on the hunt for a software engineering position in a company that will allow me to showcase my skills and grow with the company.

Outside of being a programmer, I am your typical midwestern girl from Minnesota. I was raised in Minnesota but have decided to plant my roots in San Diego, so you will definitely see or hear of me traveling back and forth.

I am also a huge family-oriented person. As my dad puts it, "If Michelle is home, that is when family and all of the kids will finally gather." I pride myself on being the self-proclaimed favorite auntie of 7 children.



Say Hello!
